可以不用web窗容器，不过让它以服务的形式一直跑，要另外加些代码，例如用`Scheduled `。

```java
@SpringBootApplication
@EnableScheduling
public class Application  {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		SpringApplication.run(Application.class, args);
	}
	@Scheduled(fixedDelay = 100000)
	public void keepRunning() {}
}
```

@SpringBootApplication
@DubboComponentScan(basePackages = {"x.xx.xxx.xxxx"})
public class Application {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        SpringApplication.run(Application.class, args);
        synchronized (Application.class) {
            while (true) {
                try {
                    Application.class.wait();
                } catch (Exception e) {
                    e.printStackTrace();
                    break;
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

基于过滤器实现把，现在大多数都是通过setAttachment实现的。
具体思路如下：
```java
//基于consumer的过滤拦截
@Activate(group = Constants.CONSUMER)
public class ConsumerFilter implements Filter{
    @Override
    public Result invoke(Invoker<?> invoker, Invocation invocation) throws RpcException {
        if (invocation instanceof RpcInvocation) {
            //自定义ThreadLocal对象获取当前的sessionID
            ((RpcInvocation) invocation).setAttachment("WebSessionID", "sessionID");
        }
        return invoker.invoke(invocation);
    }
}
//基于provider的过滤拦截
@Activate(group = Constants.PROVIDER)
public class ProviderFilter implements Filter {

    @Override
    public Result invoke(Invoker<?> invoker, Invocation invocation) throws RpcException {
        if (invocation instanceof RpcInvocation) {
            String webSessionID = ((RpcInvocation) invocation).getAttachment("WebSessionID");
            System.out.println("get sessionID from consumer is :" + webSessionID);
        }
        return invoker.invoke(invocation);
    }
}
```

